Not at all.  This puzzle contains five Fs, which is not even close to the record.  Stats have been posted only for the "Modern Era" (since Shortz became editor), and the record for F's is 12, done twice (6/12/06 and 12/20/00).

Even so, 12 is a relatively low record count for a letter.   E holds the overall record, 78, on 2/9/99, and even X has one with 16 (1/7/21).

